{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955720/extras/MAIN_GAMEPLAY.gif?t=1736182560\" /><strong>PANTHALASSA</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Panthalassa, you delve into an alien underwater world where you play as Magellan (aka MAG), an autonomous exploratory submarine who suffers a catastrophic malfunction and awakes anew, reborn in a highly advanced body, in a world they do not recognize. With technology alien to them and new emotions that were not there before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955720/extras/OFFERING_GAMEPLAY.gif?t=1736182560\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you must find out where you are, whose body you inhabit, and if there are any hopes of returning home? There'll be secrets to uncover behind an mysterious civilization and your body's previous inhabitant - you may even find out a bit more than you bargained for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955720/extras/SCOPE_GAMEPLAY-1.gif?t=1736182560\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Panthalassa is inspired by Point adventure games from the 90s and early 2000s. You see the world through the eyes of a machine and must navigate strange user interfaces where the digital and physical worlds clash. You will find new Aquatic Specimens, catalog them, solve puzzles and organically discover hidden information by searching every nook and cranny of this bizarre digital world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955720/extras/COINCIDENCE_GAMEPLAY.gif?t=1736182560\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a